
### Create a Task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Task 1",
  "description": "Description for Task 1",
  "dueDate": "2024-01-30"
}

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

### Get a Specific Task
# Replace '1' with the actual task ID you want to retrieve
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

### Update a Task
# Replace '1' with the actual task ID you want to update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task 1",
  "description": "Updated description for Task 1",
  "dueDate": "2024-02-01"
}

### Delete a Task
# Replace '1' with the actual task ID you want to delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
